data.title: William Peace University Announces Dean’s List for Spring & Summer 2019

data.text:
Our success as an institution has always been rooted in the strength of our community. As an integral part of that community, we invite alumni to stay informed and connected.

William Peace University is proud to announce its spring and summer 2019 Dean’s List recipients. These hardworking and dedicated students have achieved one of three levels, depending on certain criteria: Dean’s List, Dean’s list with Distinction, and Dean’s Scholar. Below you will find the complete lists of traditional undergraduate students, as well as students from the School of Professional Studies.

“It’s a pleasure for the faculty and staff of William Peace University to recognize the academic achievements of our students. Those students who earned a place on the Spring / Summer 2019 Dean’s List have demonstrated a commitment to academic excellence that today we are delighted to celebrate”

Dr. Charles Duncan, Vice President for Academic Affairs
